      <div class="card block">
        <figure class="card-image-wrap">
          <a href="CARD_LINK_1">
            <img alt="" src="img/CARD_IMAGE_1.png">
          </a>
        </figure>
        <div class="card-content">
          <h5 class="trailer-half leader-0">
            <a href="CARD_LINK_1">Create and share a map</a>
          </h5>
          <p>Extend the reach of ArcGIS into the field, and improve the accuracy and currency of your spatial data. Create and share maps for data collection in two steps.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="CARD_LINK_1" class="btn btn-clear btn-fill leader-0">Learn more</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card block">
        <figure class="card-image-wrap">
          <a href="CARD_LINK_2">
            <img alt="" src="img/CARD_IMAGE_2.png">
          </a>
        </figure>
        <div class="card-content">
          <h5 class="trailer-half leader-0">
            <a href="CARD_LINK_2">Collect data</a>
          </h5>
          <p>Create the data that matters to your organization, from damage reports and service requests to places of historical interest. Easily include images and videos, and share your work.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="CARD_LINK_2" class="btn btn-clear btn-fill leader-0">Learn more</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card block">
        <figure class="card-image-wrap">
          <a href="CARD_LINK_3">
            <img alt="" src="img/CARD_IMAGE_3.png">
          </a>
        </figure>
        <div class="card-content">
          <h5 class="trailer-half leader-0">
            <a href="CARD_LINK_3">Go offline</a>
          </h5>
          <p>Fieldwork takes you places without a data connection. Take your maps and data offline, collect data, and get back in sync once reconnected.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="CARD_LINK_3" class="btn btn-clear btn-fill leader-0">Learn more</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card block">
        <figure class="card-image-wrap">
          <a href="CARD_LINK_4">
            <img alt="" src="img/CARD_IMAGE_4.png">
          </a>
        </figure>
        <div class="card-content">
          <h5 class="trailer-half leader-0">
            <a href="CARD_LINK_4">Get professional-grade accuracy</a>
          </h5>
